      "content": "i tried tylenol earlier too and it didnt do much. i feel like i need something stronger if this is gonna keep me up all night. if i take another 800mg of the ibuprofen in a few hours, is that really gonna hurt me? i just need to be able to sleep and i cant do that with this pain.",
